{"tid":516351,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣被爆跟「前男友」復合","createTime":"2018-01-01T10:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T11:00:57.000Z","uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"580059d4559312e742c1e413c4801777ae2284d6","tid":516351,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"憑日劇《僱傭妻子》及電影《乒乓情人夢》令人氣爆升的新垣結衣，雖曾獲網民選為「國民妻子」，然而29歲的她，感情生活卻一片空白，直至最近有傳她跟2007年合演電影《戀空》的前緋聞男友三浦春馬秘密復合，令不少宅男粉絲震驚不已。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自從新垣跟男團「關8」成員錦戶亮分手後，盛傳她跟年輕兩歲的三浦擦出愛火，甚至已達同居關係，但遭雙方事務所否認。今年春天，三浦跟舞蹈員女友菅原小春分手，日媒爆料指「恨嫁」的新垣於夏季展開復合大計，透過短訊頻頻聯絡三浦，且看這段「姊弟戀」今次能否開花結果？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/183718_64214d1b7fac0b6520f82ed76f49ed44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F183718_64214d1b7fac0b6520f82ed76f49ed44.jpg&h=bf2ba4ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d97865e24c60281d40b506c00c9a88e538244f33","tid":516351,"uid":4525,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"又『那個』了唷"},{"pid":"5acc6c27e6a7fc8eba4a55bcccda4c2c9b259a29","tid":516351,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9287f99c0477684c34f3170f0618e69f5ade84e7","tid":516351,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"其實係我"},{"pid":"76dcdacd61f8ba6c2767f854e954ab61e8841e76","tid":516351,"uid":2777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6efabdabd2d440d377daee407bcd41e677658f8","tid":516351,"uid":30768,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"真係G黎"},{"pid":"fe1247688aeef5e169a11a133ca1d77f91e2e17a","tid":516351,"uid":103309,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三浦春馬跟朋友炫耀：「我跟新垣『那個』了~~~~唷！」</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"9d41514c8afc33f2322f3546870611b13321d985","tid":516351,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"達哥又有野ff"},{"pid":"67a09096fab1d8ced16669705907ea98b3f121d8","tid":516351,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"6b8b0485267c8f3d0c7e8870c5957ec6e3e9d120","tid":516351,"uid":82007,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9d41514c8afc33f2322f3546870611b13321d985","tid":516351,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"達哥又有野ff"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"一定係達哥為左幫兄弟做新聞，又讓條女比人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6308921fa8876dc1d873f85cdce2afab3cb44643","tid":516351,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"食過返尋味"}]}